data.description: Own this exclusive Golf Course home at a very reasonable price!! Architecturally designed for natural light; the passive solar and skylight window design offers stunning vaulted peaked ceilings throughout! Incredible mountain views, 4 main level bedrooms plus study. The large living room is located off the eat-in dining and roomy kitchen. The formal living room is located adjacent to the formal dining room, with a wonderful layout, dramatic ceilings, and for added ambiance to two spaces at once with a see-through fireplace! This home has it all! The fresh paint and carpet were selected with class. The owner's ensuite is oversized with a gracious large shower and bath area with doubleheaded rain shower, heated floor, heated towel bars, and double granite vanities. This large corner lot is conveniently located right across the street from the very nice Club House with an outdoor pool. Many amenities, including a tennis court, and of course the Walking Stick Golf Course. (Walking Stick Golf Course is one of Pueblo's pre-eminent public golf facilities and the leading major tournament venue in Pueblo.) Privacy is offered at the front lanai, and especially in the oversized rear courtyard-like area and electronic perimeter dog-fencing. This extra large home has all of the conveniences on the main level, while offering an equally large basement with an enormous storage area; a theater; snack room, plus a bedroom/workout room and a full size bathroom. Schedule a viewing today!
